comments: Ellis (SAC) avoids making contact with Brunson's (NYK) arm during his legal contest of the jump shot attempt.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Hartenstein (NYK) comes into contact with the ball while his right foot is out of bounds. Possession is properly awarded to Sacramento.
Sabonis (SAC) firms up over his left leg and marginal contact occurs as he comes together with DiVincenzo (NYK) during the pick.
Hart (NYK) momentarily rests his forearm on Sabonis (SAC) as they come together during the rebounding opportunity, and marginal contact occurs as Hart releases away from the offensive player.
Sabonis (SAC) reaches for the ball when marginal contact occurs with DiVincenzo's (NYK) right arm before Hart (NYK) retrieves the rebound.

Hart (NYK) attempts to gather the ball on his right foot but proceeds to bobble and lose control during his spin. Hart then takes several legal steps before regathering the ball and stopping before promptly making a pass.
Monk (SAC) legally contests Brunson's (NYK) jump shot attempt and any hand to hand contact after the release is considered incidental.
Sabonis (SAC) gathers the ball as he comes together with Anunoby (NYK) in the paint and Anunoby absorbs the marginal contact the end of Sabonis' dribble.
Anunoby (NYK) reaches in and comes across Sabonis' (SAC) face, affecting his SQBR in the lane.
Hartenstein (NYK) brings his arm down toward the ball and he makes contact with it and incidental hand on ball contact with Sabonis (SAC).
Sabonis (SAC) takes one dribble before gathering the ball in the paint. He then proceeds to pivot multiple times before illegally resuming his dribble.
Play is stopped due to a clock malfunction. After the correction, play resumes with Sacramento retaining possession.
Anunoby (NYK) raises his right arm up and makes clean contact with the ball, legally blocking Fox's (SAC) driving shot attempt.
Hartenstein (NYK) momentarily rests his hands on Sabonis' (SAC) sides while the shot attempt travels through the air and the contact during the rebounding opportunity is marginal.
Monk (SAC) commits a take foul on Brunson (NYK).
Sabonis (SAC) firms up in Fox's (SAC) path and does not deliver any illegal contact when setting the pick.
